 com;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;SCHEDULE-AGENT=NONE:mailto:ma
 rc.benardout@me.com
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION;LANGUAGE=en-US:Overview:\n\n  *\nScott Cohen introduced Marc 
 Benardout to Brett Johnson after learning more about Marc’s company and 
 work.\n  *\nMarc Benardout and Nicolas Rosen are founders of The Reson8 
 Frequency System\, a company focused on longevity and health technologie
 s based in the Los Angeles area.\n  *\nScott noted the company has early
  adoption from Premier League teams as part of sports medicine initiativ
 es and support from major figures in music\, including Ed Sheeran.\n  *\
 nScott believed the introduction was relevant given Brett’s involvement 
 in soccer\, including Ipswich Town.\n  *\nMarc is also involved with the
  USL franchise in Orange County\, which connects with Brett’s role as a 
 founder of Phoenix Rising FC.\n  *\nScott suggested there may be multipl
 e opportunities for collaboration across sports\, health technology\, an
 d international markets in both the U.S. and the U.K.\n\nZoom details\nh
 ttps://us02web.zoom.us/j/9253487569?pwd=QTdPR0UrMWMvZ2FVQ0tGM1luUWlLUT09
 \nMeeting ID: 925 348 7569\nPasscode: 8Z6cj6\n\nDial in number:\n+168927
 81000 US\nPasscode: 696780\n
