DESCRIPTION:\nThe address is 926 N. Sycamore Avenue\, West Hollywood on t
 he 8th floor. When you arrive at security\, let them know you're here fo
 r Minml Group.\n\nWhen you exit the elevator\, turn left to get to the o
 ffice. The office doors are locked and Rachel will buzz you in. All gues
 ts are required to sign in on Envoy at each visit\, regardless of any pr
 ior sign ins. After signing in\, guests will be issued a badge\, which m
 ust be worn throughout their visit. \n\nThere is covered parking in the 
 building. The parking rates are $1.50 Each 15 Minutes\, $15.00 Daily Max
 imum. There are also several parking facilities within walking distance 
 of our location and street parking as well.
