DESCRIPTION:<b>Please bring your ID to check into the event </b><br><br>J
 oin the Ionava team as we bring together health &amp\; wellness innovato
 rs from LA and national companies to live/work/play\, network and synerg
 ize together in one space. <br><br>The Health &amp\; Wellness Tech Innov
 ators Summit presents this powerful message: time for a revolution in ho
 w we approach\, define\, fuel\, and fund our well-being\, health\, and h
 ealthcare. <br><br>True wellness springs from the intersection of financ
 ial\, social\, personal\, spiritual\, mental and physical health. <br><b
 r>A powerful panel and guest speakers - Peter Ward\, CCO at Oura and mor
 e<br><br>Summit Agenda: <br>10am - Yoga and breath work breakout session
 s <br>10am - Co-working space open (with of course free Wifi!) <br>1pm -
  Adaptogenic coffee/tea bar opensBooths with ayurvedic nutrition experts
 Hormonal health expertsMassageAnd more <br>2-3pm - VIP health &amp\; wel
 lness Founders &amp\; VCs panel discussion <br>3-6pm - Speed networking 
 &amp\; Live DJ\, zero-proof cocktails\, demos/samples\, innovation celeb
 ration <br>6pm - Co-working closesThis is the future of work and wellnes
 s. <br><br>Hosted by:Ionava - Ionava breaks free of the traditional heal
 th insurance model and helps pay for the products and services which sup
 port everyone’s healthiest life. <br><br>This event is a part of #LATech
 Week—a week of events hosted by VCs and startups to bring together the t
 ech ecosystem. Learn more at <a href="http://www.tech-week.com/" target=
 "_blank">www.tech-week.com</a>.
