DESCRIPTION:Event Name: Web Summit Vancouver 2026: Startups Program\n\nIt
  would be great if we could have a 20 minute call to discuss your compan
 y’s future plans and having you involved in Web Summit Vancouver 2026.\n
 \n\nOnce you book a time\, a member of our team will be assigned to assi
 st you.\n\n\nThe meeting will be held on Google Meet - the team member w
 ill be at the link given at the scheduled time.\n\n\nImportant: Appointm
 ent availability is shown in your local timezone. Please ensure your dev
 ice’s timezone settings are correct before booking.\n\nLocation: This is
  a Google Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your comp
 uter\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/e2332087-6a8
 c-45d3-a33a-ecb35acc37b8/google_meet\n\nPhone number (including country 
 code): 3236978154\n\nBrief Description of Startup: Reson8 is pioneering 
 precision sound therapy grounded in genetics and backed by clinical tria
 ls. Our patented frequency system targets gene expression linked to cell
 ular repair\, stress resilience\, and neuroplasticity. From elite athlet
 es to everyday wellness seekers\, we deliver personalized audio protocol
 s that activate your body’s own healing pathways. Proven. Data-driven. D
 esigned for the future of preventative health.\n\nNeed to make changes t
 o this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/886f841b-00dd-
 4bb0-b69a-7bec5a4d84f4\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/8
